      "settings": {
        "product-description_heading": "Product Description",
        "product-description_text": "<p>The H₂ Ortigator Pod is the ultimate \"set and forget\" watering and plant protection system for anyone establishing new trees or vines. It's designed to provide a continuous, deep water supply directly to the root zone, while also protecting your young plant from weeds, pests, and the elements.</p>\n\n<p>Made in New Zealand from durable, UV-resistant plastic, the H₂ Ortigator works perfectly alongside Wool Life's Wool Mulch & Weed Mats to create the ideal growing environment. Check out www.h2ortigator.co.nz to see how you can use the H₂ Ortigator throughout your property.</p>",
