        "grid_item_GNQTNj": {
          "type": "grid-item",
          "settings": {
            "grid-item_image": "shopify://shop_images/Life-Support-Icon_f5d8f02f-d29c-4a77-b02b-5e03a03e5de9.png",
            "grid-item_heading": "A Complete Life Support System",
            "grid-item_paragraph": "<p>The H₂ Ortigator Pod is a complete life support system for your new fruit trees, natives, and ornamentals. It takes care of a number of tasks for you, including watering, weed control, and protecting your plant from pests and damage.</p>",
            "grid-item_btn-label": "",
            "grid-item_btn-link": ""
          }
        },
        "grid_item_CaBzRm": {
          "type": "grid-item",
          "settings": {
            "grid-item_image": "shopify://shop_images/Water-temp_beige_1.png",
            "grid-item_heading": "Smarter Watering System",
            "grid-item_paragraph": "<p>The H₂Ortigator Pod’s patented design delivers water slowly and directly to the roots eliminating waste, preventing over-irrigation, and ensuring steady hydration for stronger roots and less transplant shock. The most efficient way to keep trees and vines perfectly hydrated.</p>",
            "grid-item_btn-label": "",
            "grid-item_btn-link": ""
          }
        },
        "grid_item_7CxwAJ": {
          "type": "grid-item",
          "settings": {
            "grid-item_image": "shopify://shop_images/Easy_to_use_beige_1.png",
            "grid-item_heading": "Convenient & Easy to Use",
            "grid-item_paragraph": "<p>Forget timers, weeding, and guessing water volumes. This all-in-one system saves you time and effort. Simply connect it to your existing irrigation, a garden hose, or a rainwater tank. The pod refills in under two minutes, and a single fill can last up to two days.</p>",
            "grid-item_btn-label": "",
            "grid-item_btn-link": ""
          }
        },
        "grid_item_ABhiqB": {
          "type": "grid-item",
          "settings": {
            "grid-item_image": "shopify://shop_images/Promotes-plant-growth_beige_1.png",
            "grid-item_heading": "Promotes Thriving Plant Growth",
            "grid-item_paragraph": "<p>The H₂ Ortigator's unique \"little and often\" watering approach ensures consistent soil moisture, which encourages roots to grow downwards, creating a more resilient, well-established plant. The unit also shields the root zone from extreme weather, creating a stable microclimate for optimal growth.</p>",
            "grid-item_btn-label": "",
            "grid-item_btn-link": ""
          }
        },
        "grid_item_e3zKkG": {
          "type": "grid-item",
          "settings": {
            "grid-item_image": "shopify://shop_images/nz_icon_41a70ff8-5127-490c-8adf-1d97452a6729.png",
            "grid-item_heading": "A Sustainable Kiwi Investment",
            "grid-item_paragraph": "<p>Designed and manufactured in New Zealand, the pod is built for durability and endless reusability. Made from 25% recycled plastic, it is an efficient way to conserve water, with trials showing water savings of up to 60% per plant. This is a long-term investment in your garden's health and a more sustainable way to grow.</p>",
            "grid-item_btn-label": "",
            "grid-item_btn-link": ""
          }
        },
        "grid_item_rXUdNA": {
          "type": "grid-item",
          "settings": {
            "grid-item_image": "shopify://shop_images/award.png",
            "grid-item_heading": "Award-Winning Innovation",
            "grid-item_paragraph": "<p>This innovative NZ designed product has been recognised with the 2022 Innovation in Irrigation. Award from Irrigation NZ, the 2022 Fourneau Trophy for Innovation in Fruit Growing from the Fruit Growers Trust, and Best Emerging Business at the 2024 Pan Pac Hawke's Bay Business Awards</p>",
            "grid-item_btn-label": "",
            "grid-item_btn-link": ""
          }
        }
