            "grid-item_image": "shopify://shop_images/Brand_Icons-13.png",
            "grid-item_heading": "Manual Hose Fill",
            "grid-item_paragraph": "<p>Replace the 4mm barbed connection on the pod's cap with the supplied hose adapter. You can then fill the pod manually with a garden hose. A single fill provides up to 48 hours of water to the plant.</p>",
            "grid-item_btn-label": "",
            "grid-item_btn-link": ""
          }
        },
        "grid_item_xC4yEj": {
          "type": "grid-item",
          "settings": {
            "grid-item_image": "shopify://shop_images/Brand_Icons-13.png",
            "grid-item_heading": "Existing Irrigation System",
            "grid-item_paragraph": "<p>Use the supplied line punch to create a hole in your irrigation line. Insert the barbed connector and micro tubing, then connect the other end of the tubing to the pod's 4mm barb. The pod fills automatically when you run your irrigation system.</p>",
            "grid-item_btn-label": "",
            "grid-item_btn-link": ""
          }
        },
        "grid_item_L4KaaH": {
          "type": "grid-item",
          "settings": {
            "grid-item_image": "shopify://shop_images/Brand_Icons-14.png",
            "grid-item_heading": "Direct to Tap",
            "grid-item_paragraph": "<p>You can run micro tubing directly from a garden tap, but you may need a pressure regulator</p>",
            "grid-item_btn-label": "",
            "grid-item_btn-link": ""
          }
        },
        "grid_item_ajQC9y": {
          "type": "grid-item",
          "settings": {
            "grid-item_image": "shopify://shop_images/Brand_Icons-15.png",
            "grid-item_heading": "Water Tanks",
            "grid-item_paragraph": "<p>The pods can operate from low-pressure supplies like rain barrels. The water<br/>tank must be above<br/>the pod's height to operate correctly.</p>",
