        },
        "grid_item_4NJnJV": {
          "type": "grid-item",
          "settings": {
            "grid-item_image": "shopify://shop_images/Brand_Icons-13.png",
            "grid-item_heading": "Fertiliser use",
            "grid-item_paragraph": "<p>You can use fully water-soluble fertiliser with the pod. Premix the fertiliser in water<br/>before adding it to the pod, and then refill the pod with clean water after application to prevent clogs and salt buildup. Do not use non-water-soluble fertilisers.</p>",
